snippet.title: SP and BSP Urge PM Modi to Provide Quick Relief to Farmers and Common Man

localized.description:
Samajwadi Party and BSP urged PM Modi to provide quick relief to farmers and common man. Opposition parties like Congress, Left, AAP are opposing Modi government's decision of demonetising Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes.
